description: Are you thinking of a wish?  Ask the wishing well to grant a wish for you.  Think of a wish and then ask wishing well for a wish.  The magic person who lives in the wishing well will say the magic words and maybe your wish will be granted!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask wishing well for a wish.
name: Wishing Well
shortDescription: Think of a wish and then ask wishing well to grant your wish.
